properties.areaDesc: Glacier Bay; Eastern Chichagof Island; Salisbury Sound to Cape Fairweather Coastal Area
properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 25 at 9:20AM AKST until January 25 at 9:00PM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow. Additional snow accumulations of 2 to 6 inches.

* WHERE...Glacier Bay, Eastern Chichagof Island and Salisbury
Sound to Cape Fairweather Coastal Area.

* WHEN...Until 9 PM AKST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Snowfall rates may be locally moderate or
heavy this afternoon before changing to rain this evening.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 PM AKST THIS EVENING
